def: One who furthers. or helps to advance; a promoter. Shak.

A flowerless plant which forms a true fruit as the result offertilization, as the red seaweeds, the Ascomycetes, etc.
The sixteenth century, when applied to Italian art orliterature; as, the sculpture of the Cinquecento; Cinquecento style.
Partaking of the nature both of vegetable and animal matter; --a term sometimes applied to vegetable albumen and gluten, from theirresemblance to similar animal products.
A slave who led his master's children to school, and had thecharge of them generally.
The office or position of an envoy.
A bird (Nyctidromus albicollis) ranging from Texas to SouthAmerica. It is allied to the night hawk and goatsucker.
